An '''unrik''' was a piece of flesh that served as a votive to the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Yun'o|gods]]. Members of the [[Priest caste]] would carve the unrik from their own bodies and keep it alive using their [[biot]]echnology, using it as an example of their devotion to the gods they served.

